lead_paragraph: Antonio Conte has called for patience as he attempts to implement his style of play and bring an end to Chelsea's struggles that have seen them suffer back-to-back defeats against potential Premier League title rivals.

headline.print_headline: No Magic Wand Quick-Fix for Chelsea's Struggles-Conte
